Text:
I tried to make my own beats to the acapella version of Tea and Beer, available at http://munnen.handgranat.org/Idiomdrottning/idiomdrottning_vs_jean_grae-but_only_when_im_in_london.ogg

It came out a bit crowded and thick and I got that horror-movie edginess to it, but it was more of an exercise than anything else. It only took me 40 minutes. Don't critisize it to harshly, I'm still learning.
